                    <span>I enjoy John Maxwell's books because they are easy to read and uplifting.  This book has some great examples that add credibility to his assertions.  I recommend this book for a light good read.  I also strongly recommend Optimal Thinking: How to Be Your Best Self which supplies roadmaps to maximize any situation, master emotions and bring out the best in others.  </span>
                  
