                    <span>To be honest it's been a while since Maxwell has written a book worth reading, but this one makes up for his lack of material lately. The 12 practices he discusses are great ideas and the chapter on "Thinking" really got me thinking if you will. Full of great quotes and of course best read in order of the practices you can apply immediately. </span>
                  
              
